Toe Tags

While Grissom leads a group of college students on a tour of CSI, the dead "speak" while the CSIs investigate, each narrating their own case: a dead casino security guard whose luck ran out, a wife who "fell" off a cliff while hiking with her husband, a war veteran murdered on his first day back from Iraq and two neighbors whose encounter with a chainsaw ends badly. (TV-PG)

Good Morning, Miss Bliss, Save the Last Dance for Me

At a school mixer, Zack encourages a friend to ask a girl to dance -- but the girl would rather dance with Zack. Zack: Mark-Paul Gosselaar.

Absence Makes the Heart Grow... Never Mind

Holly thinks she's ready to tell Henry that she loves him, but she hesitates after she considers her lingering feelings for Vince. Meanwhile, Val's first business trip out of New York City is surprising when Peter becomes her neighbor in the hotel.
